description:
Whilst the academics in Europe had brought great reform 250 years previous, God would use a humble farmer to teach and preach about the soon return of Jesus. William Miller was hesitant at first but then surrendered to God and allowed His plan for his life to become a reality. His ministry was multi denominational and changed countless lives.
